childAltar.hintText: 3 Spiritual Stones found in Hyrule...^$0Fire Temple...^$1Deku Tree...^$2Forest Temple...^$oYe who may become a Hero...&The path to the future is open...

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Shadow Temple...^$3Dodongo's Cavern...^$4Spirit Temple...^$5Water Temple...^$6Link's Pocket...^$7Jabu-Jabu's Belly...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to find %gGreg%w.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will be&provided by Zelda once %r5&Spiritual Stones and Medallions%w&are retrieved.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonText: You'll never deflect my bolts of&energy with your sword, then shoot&me with those Light Arrows you&happen to have.
ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me&by reflecting my lightning bolts&and unleashing the arrows from&%rFire Temple%w!^And even if you do, you'll never&find the legendary blade hidden in&%rInside Ganon's Castle%w!

sheikText: I overheard Ganondorf say that he&misplaced the %yLight Arrows%w in&%rFire Temple%w.^He also stole %gthe Master Sword%w&and hid it in %rInside Ganon's&Castle%w.
dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%rthe Lost Woods%w. I will let you&have my stretching, shrinking&keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--Dampé
gregText: By the way, if you're interested,&I saw the shiniest %gGreen Rupee%w&somewhere in%g Gerudo Training&Grounds%w.^It's said to have %rmysterious&powers%w...^But then, it could just be another&regular rupee.&Oh well.
